			<div class="left">
				<h1><a href="http://maybemaimed.com/">Maybe Maimed but Never Harmed</a></h1>
				<p>Kill all humans.</p>
			</div>
		</div>

<div id="content" class="col620">


	<div class="post-1405 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-community category-personal-experience category-personal-history category-politics-of-sex category-vanilla-life tag-donna-m-hughes tag-freedom tag-sex-education clear" id="post-1405">
