Unfortunately this kind of criticism can be so disheartening but we must not let it dissuade us from doing good work. I think educating the community is the most important way to challenge these prejudices. The accusations of abuse and child slavery were absurd, in fact hollistic sex education is the best way to keep young people safe from abuse and to help them understand that any sexual activity they partake on should involve safety, respect and consent.<br />
I work doing sexual education myself and there is much evidence that young people in countries where there is good sex education are much less likely to end up with unwanted teen pregnancies and STI&#8217;s so these conservatives are really living in a fantasy world if they think not talking about these issues will make them go away!</p>
